      "title": "30 Best Plant-Based Soups & Stews",
      "description": "The very best plant-based soups and stews for the whole family! Veggie- and protein-packed, flavorful, cozy and perfect for batch cooking. Whether it’s cold outside or you want to eat more veggies and stay on a budget — plant-based soups are always a win! What’s there not to love about them? They are suitable for beginners, great for batch cooking, super versatile, nutritious, and can hide a whole bunch of veggies. They are among our favorite vegan winter recipes and make for delicious lazy and low-calorie meals! What we love most about soups is that they are so easy to customize with whatever we find in our kitchen and that’s about to go bad in a few days.",
